"word":"forms","count":1},{"word":"consider","count":1},{"word":"developing","count":1},{"word":"wants","count":1},{"word":"thinking","count":1},{"word":"anywhere","count":1},{"word":"honestly","count":1},{"word":"dreamer","count":1},{"word":"locked","count":1},{"word":"ivory","count":1},{"word":"completely","count":1},{"word":"touch","count":1},{"word":"reality","count":1},{"word":"every","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"worked","count":1},{"word":"forget","count":1},{"word":"talking","count":1},{"word":"making","count":1},{"word":"blood","count":1},{"word":"boil","count":1},{"word":"additional","count":1},{"word":"set","count":1},{"word":"step","count":1},{"word":"shutdown","count":1},{"word":"switches","count":1},{"word":"pairs","count":1},{"word":"turn","count":1},{"word":"working","count":1},{"word":"devices","count":1},{"word":"supply","count":1},{"word":"sufficient","count":1},{"word":"thanks","count":1},{"word":"duties","count":1},{"word":"whole","count":1},{"word":"lot","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Doctor Huayu, have you found him?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"A travelling salesman? The mine is closed for business today. Please come back another day.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"If you ask me, I think the old man's just taking it easy. Maintenance work like that has got to wear on his old bones.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Maybe he's hiding somewhere, watching us, muttering, \"Damn kids, can't you let me have a little peace and quiet?\"","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"I propose we all go back to our places and carry on with our jobs. The Mine has to keep functioning even with the Refinery Tower offline.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"He'll show once he gets his rest.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"These lazy new guys. I told them to hand in the work log before their shifts ended.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Pft, in one ear and out the other. Now who's going to clean up the mess if there's an accident?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Oh, {PlayerName}. What brings you here? And Huaxi?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Did Doctor Huayu send you as peacemakers? Did he find out about my fight with Modee?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Refinery Tower reboot? So you found Uncle Hong?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Ah, so that's what's going on. Uncle Hong is always so sharp and on top of things. It's hard to imagine him being anything less.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"I work alongside him all the time, and I never noticed. Alright, what do you need help with?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Well, it's not as hard as you might imagine. We have a double circuit power system at the bottom of the Mine. Either one can sustain its normal functioning.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"However, the two circuits can't run in parallel. If we force them, it could cause the breakers around the Mine to trip.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"What we can do is bring in extra external power and shut down some internal systems to focus the energy on the Refinery Tower.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Alright, I'll handle shutting down the systems. The backup mobile power sources are there at the base.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"You'll need to install them at the Refinery Tower. I'll let you know when everything's ready, okay?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Ugh, it's nothing big. Modee and I argue all the time. I'm used to it.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"I just can't stand his attitude. Everything he does, it's all some fantasy in his head.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"He's always going around the Mine, bragging about his grand philosophy of coexisting with Tacet Discords.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"He says it's a key evolutionary skill to coexist with new life forms, that we should consider developing alongside Tacet Discords.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"He can think about it all he wants, but just thinking won't get us anywhere. Honestly, he's just a dreamer, locked up in his ivory tower, completely out of touch with reality.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Every time I say something, he gets all worked up.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Forget it. Just talking about it is making my blood boil. Let's focus on the Refinery Tower.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"{PlayerName}, is the additional power set up?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Just one more step. The shutdown switches come in pairs, so I need you to turn off the other one at the same time.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"It's working. The devices are being shut down. The power supply for the Refinery Tower should be sufficient now.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Thanks for your help. If everything's good here, I'll get back to my duties.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Got a whole lot of things to do. Please carry on with the good work with the Refinery Tower.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003}]}